Package: arc-osx-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 paper-icon-theme
Description: Icon theme that complements OSX-Arc Theme collection
 OSX-Arc-Collection is a flat theme collection with transparent
 elements for GTK+ 3, GTK+ 2 which supports desktop environments 
 like GNOME, Unity, Budgie, Pantheon, Xfce, MATE, etc.
 .
 The Arc-OSX-Icon-Theme contains two iconsets, one for
 the darker themes and the other for the lighter themes
